msgstr "发展模式"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2020-05-05-introducing-command-mode.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Command mode works with `quarkus:dev` aka. dev-mode."
msgstr "命令模式与 `quarkus:dev` aka.dev-mode一起工作。"

